1201
01:14:25,842 --> 01:14:28,050
You're gonna tell them
what I did.

1202
01:14:29,092 --> 01:14:32,423
The man with the tattoos,

1203
01:14:32,425 --> 01:14:36,508
he was gonna steal things
from my home.

1204
01:14:41,592 --> 01:14:43,298
Guy!

1205
