1215
01:15:08,842 --> 01:15:10,675
Don't tell anyone.

1216
01:15:14,550 --> 01:15:15,840
Prisca!

1217
01:15:15,842 --> 01:15:18,425
Hide the kids! I'll protect you!

1218
01:15:22,717 --> 01:15:24,381
Yes.

1219
01:15:24,383 --> 01:15:26,673
Maddox! Trent!

1220
01:15:26,675 --> 01:15:30,423
