1266
01:21:27,258 --> 01:21:31,425
Well, whatever it was, uh,
I'm not mad anymore.

1267
01:21:39,300 --> 01:21:41,175
I can't remember.

1268
01:21:45,842 --> 01:21:48,508
Why did we want
to leave this beach?

1269
01:21:54,550 --> 01:21:56,467
So beautiful.

1270
01:22:00,508 --> 01:22:02,425
